# ============================================
# NanDe Garden - Privacy Protection
# 私人数据绝不上传
# ============================================

# 用户碎片日记 (Private Fragments)
fragments/**/*.md
!fragments/README.md

# 存档数据 (Private Archives)
archives/**/*.md
!archives/README.md

# 火花辩论记录 (Private Sparks)
sparks/**/*.md

# 时刻记录 (Private Moments)
moments/**/*.md

# 保留目录结构
!**/.gitkeep

# ============================================
# 系统文件
# ============================================
.DS_Store
*.pyc
__pycache__/
.env
*.log
